	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I didn't realize that any of the mappers supporting CHR banking lack PRG banking, so having access to CHR banking would be a trade-off for having half the total PRG size. That seems like a fair trade. I'll be sticking to UNROM for the 64KB.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


