		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You could also target MMC1 with CHR banking set to the 8KB mode and use that during development if the emulators you use don't support mapper 28, and switch it over once your game is all debugged and finished.<br /><br />Edit: Though you would probably need to use CHR ROM, and switch it over to CHR RAM.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
